---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about SIP Protocol - the privacy standard for Web3"
>
  <article class="about-page">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1>About SIP Protocol</h1>
      <p class="tagline">The Privacy Standard for Web3</p>
    </header>

    <section class="mission">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        SIP (Shielded Intents Protocol) is building the privacy layer for Web3 ‚Äî like HTTPS for the
        internet. One toggle to shield sender, amount, and recipient using stealth addresses,
        Pedersen commitments, and viewing keys for compliance.
      </p>
      <p>
        We believe privacy is a fundamental right, not a feature. That's why we're creating
        middleware that sits between applications and blockchains, making any transaction private
        while maintaining compliance capabilities for institutions that need them.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="technology">
      <h2>The Technology</h2>
      <div class="tech-grid">
        <div class="tech-item">
          <h3>Stealth Addresses</h3>
          <p>One-time recipient addresses that prevent transaction linkability and protect recipient privacy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-item">
          <h3>Pedersen Commitments</h3>
          <p>Cryptographic commitments that hide transaction amounts while enabling verification.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-item">
          <h3>Viewing Keys</h3>
          <p>Selective disclosure for compliance ‚Äî share transaction details with auditors without exposing everything.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-item">
          <h3>Chain Agnostic</h3>
          <p>Works across Solana, Ethereum, NEAR, and more. One privacy layer, settle anywhere.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="blog-about">
      <h2>About This Blog</h2>
      <p>
        This blog is where we share technical deep-dives, ecosystem updates, tutorials, and our
        vision for privacy in Web3. Whether you're a developer looking to integrate SIP, or someone
        interested in blockchain privacy, you'll find valuable content here.
      </p>
      <div class="categories">
        <h3>What We Write About</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/category/technical/">Technical</a> ‚Äî Architecture, specs, implementation details</li>
          <li><a href="/category/tutorials/">Tutorials</a> ‚Äî Step-by-step guides and code examples</li>
          <li><a href="/category/ecosystem/">Ecosystem</a> ‚Äî Partnerships and integrations</li>
          <li><a href="/category/thought-leadership/">Thought Leadership</a> ‚Äî Privacy philosophy and trends</li>
          <li><a href="/category/announcements/">Announcements</a> ‚Äî Releases and news</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="links">
      <h2>Learn More</h2>
      <div class="link-grid">
        <a href="https://sip-protocol.org" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="link-icon">üåê</span>
          <span class="link-title">Website</span>
          <span class="link-desc">sip-protocol.org</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://docs.sip-protocol.org" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="link-icon">üìö</span>
          <span class="link-title">Documentation</span>
          <span class="link-desc">docs.sip-protocol.org</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/sip-protocol" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="link-icon">üíª</span>
          <span class="link-title">GitHub</span>
          <span class="link-desc">github.com/sip-protocol</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://x.com/sipprotocol" class="link-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="link-icon">ùïè</span>
          <span class="link-title">Twitter/X</span>
          <span class="link-desc">@sipprotocol</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sip-primary), var(--sip-accent));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: rgb(var(--gray));
    margin: 0;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: rgb(var(--black));
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: rgb(var(--black));
  }

  p {
    color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .tech-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tech-item {
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .tech-item h3 {
    color: var(--sip-primary);
  }

  .tech-item p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: rgb(var(--gray));
  }

  .categories ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .categories li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
    color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .categories li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .categories a {
    color: var(--sip-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .categories a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .link-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .link-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .link-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--sip-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
  }

  .link-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .link-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgb(var(--black));
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .link-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgb(var(--gray));
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .tech-grid,
    .link-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
